The paper discusses multiuser coding techniques for mismatched decoding, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network communication (cs.NI). The paper also mentions the use of coding techniques for improving the performance of communication systems (cs.SI), and the use of algorithms for decoding (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG).
